title: Amazon Expected to Post Strong Quarterly Profit
description: Analysts anticipate the company’s results will show improving consumer e-commerce business, but investors also are watching a slowdown in cloud computing.

title: Apple Sees Third Straight Quarter of Falling Sales, Longest Slump Since 2016
description: Sales of iPhones missed analyst estimates, but revenue in the company services unit reached a record high.

title: Meta's Ray-Ban Smart Glasses Fail to Catch On
description: The company plans the release of the second generation as less than 10% of the devices purchased are used monthly, an internal company document shows.
